  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--not in its true detail sense, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, from Arlo, as I said, end July, or I think it was end July, we were the, the battalion, which was [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]-- 101 per 302.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the-- my battalion's name, 101 dash 302.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, look, I mean, there were hundreds of such battalions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that, that, you know, that identified that battalion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went-- we came up to, to Budapest, which was very, very lucky.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have been very lucky in our movements because we could have been just as easily taken out to the Ukraine, as a lot of other people have been.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And luck has a lot to do with one's survival.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have learned that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they have-- they have say in the day-to-day running of things, yes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But not in the movements.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- no, no, no, not even the-- not even the, the, the battalion leader, who was a lieutenant, you know, he would have been a, a reserve soldier who has been called in, who has been a, a, a country teacher, very quite a decent human being would, would-- that came out of the blue, and, you know.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we moved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came up to, to Pest, to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have been installed in a building near [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was a-- was a [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] rail [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] center where, you know, where, where supply came in, where supply have been reloaded and re-dispatched some other areas.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a rather important regional rail center.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
